The paper deals with channel estimation and data detection in wireless communication systems, which is a topic closely related to information theory (cs.IT). The proposed algorithm and VLSI designs involve optimization techniques and hardware implementation, which are relevant to computer architecture (cs.AR) and embedded systems (cs.ET). The paper also discusses convergence analysis and performance evaluation, which are related to control systems (cs.SY) and machine learning (cs.LG).
